### Add product to the cart
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}



### Get the cart
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### Clear the cart
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}